quran[9{c,v,t}:
40,50,woh kahin ge kekiya tumahray paas tumahray paighambar nishanain le kar nahi aeye they. woh kahin ge kyun nahi to woh kahin ge ke tum hi dua karo. aur kafiroon ki dua ( is roz ) be car hogi
40,51,hum apne payghambaroon ki aur jo log imaan laaye hain un ki duniya ki zindagi mein bhi madad karte hain aur jis din gawah kharray hon ge ( yani qayamat ko bhi )
40,52,jis din zaalmon ko un ki moazrat kuch faida nah day gi aur un ke liye laanat aur bura ghar hai
40,53,aur hum ne moose ko hadaayat ( ki kitaab ) di aur bani Israel ko is kitaab ka waris banaya
40,54,aqal walon ke liye hadaayat aur nasiyaat hai
40,55,to sabr karo be shak khuda ka wada sacha hai aur apne gunaaho ki maffi mango aur subah vsham apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh karte raho
40,56,jo log baghair kisi Daleel ke jo un ke paas aayi ho khuda ki aayton mein jhagarte hain un ke dilon mein aur kuch nahi (iradah ) Azmat hai aur woh is ko pounchanay walay nahi to khuda ki panah mango. be shak woh suneney wala ( aur ) dekhnay wala hai
40,57,asmano aur zameen ka peda karna logon ke peda karne ki nisbat bara ( kaam ) hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
40,58,aur andha aur aankhh wala barabar nahi. aur nah imaan laane walay nekokaar aur nah badkaar ( barabar hain ) ( haqeeqat yeh hai ke ) tum bohat kam ghhor karte ho
